{"tid":499263,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]讀左周易幾年，你問我答","createTime":"2017-12-14T15:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T21:40:18.000Z","uid":107938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fdab476dea2d4c7d1788f940c7de618a0fd1b144","tid":499263,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"之前都開過帖講周易，不過沉左底，而家重開。任何有關周易既問題，都歡迎問我，如果係同訓詁歷史有關就更好。另外提提大家，唔好罵戰。之前試過有網友嘈易經係唔係迷信，呢啲交嘈來好無謂，有時間解多易經幾隻字好過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296ff888fa3d1abd88ab70f9e6f386d3d5daf4aa","tid":499263,"uid":9040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"有咩方法去記爻辭"},{"pid":"1a62f24622fed002e8a58b5650a857afe137a67e","tid":499263,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩方法去記爻辭</blockquote><br />\n你喺想背誦？其實就無乜好方法，試下每個卦嘅爻辭寫張紙仔，一共六十四張，咁樣應該容易記。"},{"pid":"aba561fbaadd1552083e328a1d161b90aaffb056","tid":499263,"uid":145472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"1)有無邊本書係信得過？<br />\n之前跟個阿 sir 叫我地唔好亂睇坊間易經書，好多錯。<br />\n<br />\n2) 有無邊幾句易經係係成日講，或者對你人生最有得著？<br />\n<br />\n小弟只係學過少少易，學道理為主。自己好鐘意 &ldquo;時行則行，時止則止。動靜不失其時，其道光明&rdquo; 呢一句，覺得好順口好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b96df0d285aaee15cce6b79cb31ad5a087be5e5","tid":499263,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1)有無邊本書係信得過？<br />\n之前跟個阿 sir 叫我地唔好亂睇坊間易經書，好多錯。<br />\n<br />\n2) 有無邊幾句易經係係成日講，或者對你人生最有得著？<br />\n<br />\n小弟只係學過少少易，學道理為主。自己好鐘意 &ldquo;時行則行，時止則止。動靜不失其時，其道光明&rdquo; 呢一句，覺得好順口好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一，打底可以睇高亨先生既周易古經今注，主要係學佢既方法，用訓詁學史學禮學去證易經。不過佢既結論唔可以盡信，例如亢龍有悔佢就解錯。睇完呢本，再有唔明可以問我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二，最鍾意都係潛龍勿用呢句，做人既嘢，唔係下下順風順水，要修德以俟時。"},{"pid":"df24378b99e64abcf53ca37625704dfdb1b7301d","tid":499263,"uid":90036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"你所講既解錯係指咩?指佢解釋個坑字錯左，定係指佢成句理解錯左?"},{"pid":"7206cd828926cf5f40e482845c3d5e8cf9fbd179","tid":499263,"uid":90036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"打錯字，亢先岩"},{"pid":"416a9e181ec0b0f9ad4dba56de05ec254113ff96","tid":499263,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"有無用易經去占卜"},{"pid":"ae1a889c9c53e57988d061eeef34a76ca15e0d67","tid":499263,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"周易除左占有乜其他主要用處?"},{"pid":"9067e505dab1cd3afe4cdbc5065ae327fdef12c3","tid":499263,"uid":54867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"點去定義個作者解錯？ 以一般大眾解法去決定？"},{"pid":"88029f5f0e2e0ee2b0ab453c0030bf0d5986e0cb","tid":499263,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"乜都唔識想入門應該點做？"},{"pid":"3ca3b902b02a09d6020dd52faddfaa9ff8474826","tid":499263,"uid":58911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"唔知除左周易之外 巴打仲有無涉獵宋明理學呢？"},{"pid":"b17fe448929dcd788d6c8d65951b94e9e41d1bdc","tid":499263,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你所講既解錯係指咩?指佢解釋個坑字錯左，定係指佢成句理解錯左?</blockquote><br />\n佢解錯個亢字，認為亢通沆澤之沆，其實亢係解高亢嘅亢。解錯一隻字，成句理解就錯左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa7c7473993026da8c27dbbe532607d7c147be2","tid":499263,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:32:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無用易經去占卜</blockquote><br />\n有呀，不過好少攞來占卜，我鍾意研究當中嘅訓詁歷史多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf668091ff5318f401beec0ec3188a634391bbc","tid":499263,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周易除左占有乜其他主要用處?</blockquote><br />\n對古人來講，易經就係一本占卜書。大約從春秋時代開始，大家開始從義理角度去睇易經。咁做係好嘅，但唔好求之過深。"},{"pid":"8a582881c4f7e8a0fdbfd4d435c3064656f18a13","tid":499263,"uid":56334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"咁岩剛剛開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇梗台灣個曾仕強教授既講解<br />\n有無咩書推介？"},{"pid":"877d0de5f7b1c461cd6e0452de1e820d8562c9a5","tid":499263,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"周易點睇女人"},{"pid":"cfb371235f87b04c56a554e3bde7f9549e8cefe3","tid":499263,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T19:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周易點睇女人</blockquote><br />\n坤卦"},{"pid":"163b011c69c0ce8cd85c4de6640bf12dc3fefa54","tid":499263,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T20:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>周易點睇女人</blockquote><br />\n坤卦</blockquote><br />\n其實有冇缺失意味，即因為無jj<br />\n<br />\n就將女人認為是陰、坤"},{"pid":"c5bb7bbe3aefcb06b09f0f46cb94d2f783b09fea","tid":499263,"uid":16657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T20:34:11.000Z","msg":"學易後 有應用於生活上？"},{"pid":"a08d48e99324aa19364b4c84aba77412d89d0c68","tid":499263,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:02:32.000Z","msg":"其實討論下是否迷信都係好事黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大不了咪信錯左，承認浪費左自己幾年人生"},{"pid":"3d939e0059a13f36416541f73754e1c8deca4ac5","tid":499263,"uid":27561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:11:34.000Z","msg":"善卜者不卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b8d96e2fc4aafb1d94580ec963bd6053d11950","tid":499263,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:40:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}